headline: Morgan Stanley (MS): Evaluating Valuation After Strategic Push Into Private Markets and EquityZen Acquisition
summary: Morgan Stanley is making moves into the private markets by launching a specialized research hub focused on private companies. The firm is also entering an agreement to acquire the private shares platform EquityZen. These steps aim to address investors' growing appetite for data and access around high-growth startups.
